posting_body: ['YES, WE ARE OPEN!', 'CALL NOW TO SCHEDULE AN IN-PERSON TOUR!', 'OR LET US SHOW YOU THROUGH FACETIME!', "Conveniently located in Westminster, Colorado, halfway between Denver's central business district and Boulder County and ensconced against breathtaking and idyllic mountain scenery, Westcliff Apartments will not disappoint!", "Featuring one, two and three bedroom apartment homes with stainless steel appliances, upgraded kitchens and the largest square footage in the area, Westcliff is Westminster's premiere apartment community.", 'Call or visit us today!', 'Amenities Include:', 'Wine Room', 'Library & Reading Lounge', 'Expansive mountain views', 'Pet-friendly community with fenced in dog park', 'Vaulted Ceilings on Upper Floors', 'Built-in Bookcases', 'Fireplaces in 2nd and 3rd story homes', "9' ceilings", 'Gazebo with a Fire Pit & Gas Grill', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Outdoor Spa', 'Brand New Hardwood Floors', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
